{"id": "igz1764054370664", "title": "[OBSERVABILITY]", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "Configuration Reference", "Configuration Settings: Assignment", "[OBSERVABILITY]"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/igz1764054370664.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">[OBSERVABILITY]</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: [NET_SETTINGS]  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: [NET_SETTINGS]  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hyi1665702739258.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: [PATHS]  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: [PATHS]  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gbz1665702543976.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/igz1764054370664.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/igz1764054370664.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/igz1764054370664.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_24136698\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_24136698\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 27, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104igz1764054370664.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/igz1764054370664.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/igz1764054370664.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"igz1764054370664\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use [OBSERVABILITY] section to control the behavior of the observability feature in\n\t\tUniface. If the observability settings are not explicitly configured, the default settings\n\t\tare applied.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"igz1764054370664__section_w80ab1b5b1_w81ab1b5_w82ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d312459e49\">Syntax</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">[SETTINGS]</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Setting {{=} Value}</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104igz1764054370664_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"igz1764054370664__codeblock_jg1_1gz_khc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[OBSERVABILITY]\nTRACE = on\nTRACE_ENDPOINT = http://localhost:4318/v1/traces</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"igz1764054370664__section_hrz_bgz_khc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d312459e70\">Arguments</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"igz1764054370664__ul_b5w_xgz_khc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Setting</span>: Name of the setting.</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Value</span>: Value of the setting. If not specified, the\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdefault value is used. Refer to the individual assignment settings for their\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdefault values.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"igz1764054370664__section_yfc_dgz_khc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d312459e92\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use in the assignment files of client applications, Uniface servers.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"igz1764054370664__section_ogd_dgz_khc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d312459e101\">Description</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">The [OBSERVABILITY] section controls Uniface’s observability feature, which exports telemetry\n\t\t\t\tdata, such as traces and logs, to compatible backends to the OpenTelemetry (OTel)\n\t\t\t\t\tstandard.<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"igz1764054370664__ul_jlk_3hz_khc\">\n<li class=\"li\">Traces provide insight into ProcScript execution flow and latency.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Logs export putmess messages for debugging.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Optional enrichment settings allow adding more data to spans.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Span processing settings (queue size, batch size, schedule delay) help tune\n\t\t\t\t\t\tthroughput and latency.</li>\n</ul></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"igz1764054370664__section_f42_dgz_khc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d312459e124\">Example: Enable Traces and Logs</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104igz1764054370664_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"igz1764054370664__codeblock_dsj_5gz_khc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[OBSERVABILITY]\nTRACE = on\nLOG = on\nTRACE_ENDPOINT = http://yourhost:port/v1/traces\nLOG_ENDPOINT = http://yourhost:port/v1/logs\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"igz1764054370664__section_cn3_ggz_khc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d312459e137\">Example: Set a different service name and service role</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104igz1764054370664_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"igz1764054370664__codeblock_bs5_rgz_khc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[OBSERVABILITY]\nTRACE = on\nLOG = on\nTRACE_ENDPOINT = http://yourhost:port/v1/traces\nLOG_ENDPOINT = http://yourhost:port/v1/logs\nSERVICE_NAME=Accounting\nSERVICE_ROLE=server\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"igz1764054370664__section_ulr_ggz_khc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d312459e149\">Example: Enable Traces with additional telemetry data to spans</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104igz1764054370664_html_3\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"igz1764054370664__codeblock_j5f_pgz_khc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[OBSERVABILITY]\nTRACE = on\nTRACE_ENDPOINT = http://yourhost:port/v1/traces\n; Add $status as span attribute\nADD_PROC_STATUS = on\n; Add $proc_error as span attribute\nADD_PROC_ERROR = on\n; Add ProcScript profiling as span attributes\nADD_PROCPROFILING = on\n; Add ProcScript tracing as span events\nADD_PROCTRACING = on\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"igz1764054370664__section_qyd_jgz_khc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d312459e161\">Configuration Settings</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"igz1764054370664__table_xrw_j2z_khc\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:132\"/><col style=\"width:85\"/><col style=\"width:151\"/><col style=\"width:233\"/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Setting</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Value Type</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Default value</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">TRACE</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Off</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Enable trace telemetry (on/off). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">LOG</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Off</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Enable logging telemetry (on/off). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">SERVICE_ROLE</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Defaults depend on how the application is started, e.g.:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"igz1764054370664__ul_psh_v3z_khc\">\n<li class=\"li\">Starting with uniface executable → defaults to client</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Starting with userver executable → defaults to server</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Otherwise → defaults to internal</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Description: Role of the service (client, server, internal).\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">SERVICE_NAME</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Uniface_App</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Logical name of your service (used for grouping spans/logs).\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">TRACE_ENDPOINT</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">http://localhost:4318/v1/traces</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">OTLP HTTP endpoint for traces. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">LOG_ENDPOINT</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">http://localhost:4318/v1/logs</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">OTLP HTTP endpoint for logs. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">QUEUE_SIZE</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">2048</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Max spans in the buffer. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">BATCH_SIZE</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">512</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Max spans per batch. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">SCHEDULE_DELAY</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">5000</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Time (ms) between exports. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">FLUSH_TIMEOUT</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">5000</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Max time (ms) to flush spans on shutdown. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">ADD_PROC_STATUS</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Off</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Add $status value as Trace span attribute</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">ADD_PROC_ERROR</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Off</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Add $proc_error value as Trace span attribute</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">ADD_PROC_PROFILING</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Off</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Add <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ukx1665702707424.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ukx1665702707424.html\" title=\"ProcScript profiling enables you to analyze performance problems by logging trigger processing time. ProcScript tracing enables you to log the ProcScript that was executed, optionally enhanced with additional information.\">ProcScript Profiling and Tracing</a> data as Trace span\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tattributes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">ADD_PROC_TRACING</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Off</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Add <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ukx1665702707424.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ukx1665702707424.html\" title=\"ProcScript profiling enables you to analyze performance problems by logging trigger processing time. ProcScript tracing enables you to log the ProcScript that was executed, optionally enhanced with additional information.\">ProcScript Profiling and Tracing</a> data as Trace span events. </p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"igz1764054370664__note_f4v_qhz_khc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"igz1764054370664__ul_dv2_rhz_khc\">\n<li class=\"li\">This option is unavailable if your Uniface\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tapplication is compiled with /nodebug.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Enabling this may impact performance—use with\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcaution.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_24136698\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_24136698\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[OBSERVABILITY] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 27, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Use [OBSERVABILITY] section to control the behavior of the observability feature in Uniface. If the observability settings are not explicitly configured, the default settings are applied. Syntax [SETTINGS] Setting {{=} Value} For example: Explain this code [OBSERVABILITY] TRACE = on TRACE_ENDPOINT = http://localhost:4318/v1/traces Copy Arguments Setting : Name of the setting. Value : Value of the setting. If not specified, the default value is used. Refer to the individual assignment settings for their default values. Use Use in the assignment files of client applications, Uniface servers. Description The [OBSERVABILITY] section controls Uniface’s observability feature, which exports telemetry data, such as traces and logs, to compatible backends to the OpenTelemetry (OTel) standard. Traces provide insight into ProcScript execution flow and latency. Logs export putmess messages for debugging. Optional enrichment settings allow adding more data to spans. Span processing settings (queue size, batch size, schedule delay) help tune throughput and latency. Example: Enable Traces and Logs Explain this code [OBSERVABILITY] TRACE = on LOG = on TRACE_ENDPOINT = http://yourhost:port/v1/traces LOG_ENDPOINT = http://yourhost:port/v1/logs Copy Example: Set a different service name and service role Explain this code [OBSERVABILITY] TRACE = on LOG = on TRACE_ENDPOINT = http://yourhost:port/v1/traces LOG_ENDPOINT = http://yourhost:port/v1/logs SERVICE_NAME=Accounting SERVICE_ROLE=server Copy Example: Enable Traces with additional telemetry data to spans Explain this code [OBSERVABILITY] TRACE = on TRACE_ENDPOINT = http://yourhost:port/v1/traces ; Add $status as span attribute ADD_PROC_STATUS = on ; Add $proc_error as span attribute ADD_PROC_ERROR = on ; Add ProcScript profiling as span attributes ADD_PROCPROFILING = on ; Add ProcScript tracing as span events ADD_PROCTRACING = on Copy Configuration Settings Setting Value Type Default value Description TRACE Boolean Off Enable trace telemetry (on/off). LOG Boolean Off Enable logging telemetry (on/off). SERVICE_ROLE String Defaults depend on how the application is started, e.g.: Starting with uniface executable → defaults to client Starting with userver executable → defaults to server Otherwise → defaults to internal Description: Role of the service (client, server, internal). SERVICE_NAME String Uniface_App Logical name of your service (used for grouping spans/logs). TRACE_ENDPOINT String http://localhost:4318/v1/traces OTLP HTTP endpoint for traces. LOG_ENDPOINT String http://localhost:4318/v1/logs OTLP HTTP endpoint for logs. QUEUE_SIZE Numeric 2048 Max spans in the buffer. BATCH_SIZE Numeric 512 Max spans per batch. SCHEDULE_DELAY Numeric 5000 Time (ms) between exports. FLUSH_TIMEOUT Numeric 5000 Max time (ms) to flush spans on shutdown. ADD_PROC_STATUS Boolean Off Add $status value as Trace span attribute ADD_PROC_ERROR Boolean Off Add $proc_error value as Trace span attribute ADD_PROC_PROFILING Boolean Off Add ProcScript Profiling and Tracing data as Trace span attributes ADD_PROC_TRACING Boolean Off Add ProcScript Profiling and Tracing data as Trace span events. Note: This option is unavailable if your Uniface application is compiled with /nodebug. Enabling this may impact performance—use with caution. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}